<view class="page">
  <view class="section-card banner-card">
    <view class="section-kicker">DISCOVER</view>
    <view class="banner-title">附近商家</view>
    <view class="banner-copy">这里可以先游客浏览。允许定位后排序会更准确；不允许也没关系，仍然可以按商家名搜索并查看包间。</view>

    <view class="search-card">
      <input
        class="field-control"
        placeholder-class="field-placeholder"
        placeholder="搜索商家名称"
        value="{{keyword}}"
        bindinput="handleKeyword"
        confirm-type="search"
        bindconfirm="searchMerchants"
      />
      <button class="primary-button search-button" bindtap="searchMerchants">搜索</button>
    </view>
    <view class="helper-text">只有在真正提交预订时，才需要填写联系人和手机号。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-header">
      <view>
        <view class="section-kicker">LIST</view>
        <view class="section-title">商家列表</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="empty-card">正在获取商家...</view>

    <block wx:if="{{!loading && merchants.length}}">
      <block wx:for="{{merchants}}" wx:key="id">
        <view class="merchant-card-mini" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="openMerchant">
          <view class="pill-row">
            <view class="ghost-pill">{{item.distanceText}}</view>
            <view class="ghost-pill">{{item.roomSummary}}</view>
            <view class="ghost-pill">{{item.businessHours}}</view>
          </view>
          <view class="card-head">
            <view>
              <view class="card-title">{{item.name}}</view>
              <view class="card-subtitle">{{item.city}} · {{item.district}}</view>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="helper-text">{{item.address}}</view>
          <view class="feature-row">
            <block wx:for="{{item.featuredTags}}" wx:key="*this">
              <view class="tag">{{item}}</view>
            </block>
          </view>
          <view class="card-actions">
            <button class="primary-button button-flex" data-id="{{item.id}}" catchtap="openMerchant">查看包间</button>
          </view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </block>

    <view wx:if="{{!loading && !merchants.length}}" class="empty-card">暂时没有找到符合条件的商家。可以换个关键词，或者直接浏览全部商家。</view>
  </view>
</view>
